01:08:14,790 --> 01:08:17,224
How about some more up-downs, Huard?

721
01:08:50,025 --> 01:08:54,758
What? I'm a plebe. I love rolling
on the ground and freezing my ass off.

722
01:08:59,101 --> 01:09:02,127
