out here tonight, huh?

723
01:09:02,738 --> 01:09:05,070
- Oorah!
<i>- (plebes)</i> Oorah!

724
01:09:05,207 --> 01:09:07,675
- Oorah!
<i>- (plebes)</i> Oorah!

725
01:09:13,849 --> 01:09:16,613
Good. Time.

726
01:09:16,685 --> 01:09:19,381
- Nicely done, Huard.
- Thank you.

727
01:09:20,789 --> 01:09:25,954
Good job. Your left hook's getting there.

728
01:09:27,296 --> 01:09:29,526
- It's getting there?
- Mm-hm.

729
01:09:29,598 --> 01:09:31,930
- But it's not there yet?
- Not yet.

730
01:09:32,001 --> 01:09:33,992
- Really?
- Almost.

731
01:09:35,037 --> 01:09:38,097
- Why don't you show me? There.
- OK.

732
01:09:38,174 --> 01:09:40,165
- Not bad.
- All right.

733
01:09:40,242 --> 01:09:43,405
- Show me how to...
- It's just... the little things.

734
01:09:43,479 --> 01:09:47,540
Like, really get your weight behind it.
You know what I mean?

735
01:09:47,616 --> 01:09:51,211
Ooh! I'm so sorry! I'm so sorry.

736
01:09:51,287 --> 01:09:52,618
Oh...

737
01:09:52,688 --> 01:09:56,715
- Jeez.
- Let me see. No, it's OK. I'm sorry.

738
01:09:56,792 --> 01:09:58,555
- Is it bleeding?
- Uh-uh.

739
01:09:58,627 --> 01:10:00,618
- Huh?
- Mm-mm.

740
01:10:06,135 --> 01:10:09,366
- I'm sorry.
- That's all right.

741
01:10:09,438 --> 01:10:13,169
- I'm OK.
- No, I mean about...

742
01:10:14,710 --> 01:10:16,803
About stopping.

743
01:10:17,813 --> 01:10:19,280
Oh.

744
01:10:19,348 --> 01:10:22,943
Well, why are you sorry?
I was the one who stopped.

745
01:10:24,053 --> 01:10:25,884
What did you say?

746
01:10:25,955 --> 01:10:28,890
It was getting a little hot.
I had to push you away.

747
01:10:29,391 --> 01:10:35,261
You know what? I think I hit you
over the head a little too hard there, Jake.

748
01:10:45,708 --> 01:10:49,838
One, two, three, four,

749
01:10:49,912 --> 01:10:52,745
five, six, seven,

750
01:10:52,815 --> 01:10:56,046
eight, nine, ten.

751
01:10:56,118 --> 01:10:57,813
You're out!

752
01:11:04,593 --> 01:11:06,060
You OK?

753
01:11:09,898 --> 01:11:12,423
Nice smile, Huard.

754
01:11:12,501 --> 01:11:15,732
Can't wait to see
what Cole does to it in the finals.

755
01:11:15,804 --> 01:11:17,897
Good fight.

756
01:11:44,800 --> 01:11:47,132
No way.

757
01:12:19,368 --> 01:12:25,170
It's impressive, to be able to say
you helped build something like this.

758
01:12:48,364 --> 01:12:49,888
Take ten.

759
01:12:55,871 --> 01:12:57,736
Hey.

760
01:12:58,307 --> 01:13:00,332
The ship looks great.

761
01:13:00,409 --> 01:13:02,001
Yeah, it might float.

762
01:13:03,712 --> 01:13:07,614
So, I know you're probably busy, but...

763
01:13:07,683 --> 01:13:10,584
I have a fight next week. Saturday.

764
01:13:10,652 --> 01:13:14,850
It's the finals in the Brigades.
It's for the whole academy.

765
01:13:14,923 --> 01:13:17,391
We're still a little behind.

766
01:13:17,459 --> 01:13:19,450
Yeah. I get it.

767
01:13:21,630 --> 01:13:23,860
All right.

768
01:13:23,932 --> 01:13:26,628
I guess I'll see you soon.

769
01:13:28,237 --> 01:13:30,603
Yeah, sure.

770
01:13:30,672 --> 01:13:34,233
- Take care of yourself.
- All right. You too.

771
01:13:43,085 --> 01:13:46,816
The required time for plebes
is five minutes.

772
01:13:46,889 --> 01:13:52,020
Failure to meet that requirement
will result in separation.

773
01:13:52,094 --> 01:13:54,927
There will be no retest.

774
01:13:54,997 --> 01:13:56,988
Good luck.

775
01:13:57,966 --> 01:13:59,957
<i>(whistle)</i>

776
01:14:00,936 --> 01:14:02,995
<i>(whistle)</i>

777
