This is nothing.
You're there. You're there.

779
01:14:35,270 --> 01:14:38,364
Put it over. Put it over.
Hook it over.

780
01:14:39,775 --> 01:14:43,575
Come on. You got it.
Come on, duck down. You got it.

781
01:14:43,645 --> 01:14:46,637
Come on, that's it. Let's go. Let's go.

782
01:14:46,715 --> 01:14:48,706
That's it. You got it.

783
01:14:49,618 --> 01:14:54,021
Come on, Twins.
Show Whitaker. Show him. Let's go.

784
01:14:54,089 --> 01:14:57,581
Yeah! That's it.
Last one. Last one.

785
01:15:12,474 --> 01:15:16,672
<i>- (Loo)</i> Nice! Good job, Nance.
- Good job, man.

786
01:15:16,745 --> 01:15:18,576
<i>(Cole)</i> Nance.

787
01:15:18,647 --> 01:15:22,640
5:04. You're four seconds over.

788
01:15:27,189 --> 01:15:29,749
Sir, give him another chance.
He can make it.

789
01:15:29,825 --> 01:15:32,055
5:04 is 5:04.

790
01:15:32,127 --> 01:15:36,393
It's four seconds.
You know how far he's come?

791
01:16:01,957 --> 01:16:03,948
Hey.

792
01:16:06,895 --> 01:16:10,854
They gave me the key to the city.
You know that?

793
01:16:11,433 --> 01:16:14,129
You think I have to give it back?

794
01:16:14,670 --> 01:16:18,436
Hey, this isn't over.
We can talk to Burton.

795
01:16:20,442 --> 01:16:23,775
Remember how I told you about
that bully I beat up in the fourth grade?

796
01:16:23,845 --> 01:16:25,608
Mm-hm.

797
01:16:27,849 --> 01:16:33,913
Truth is, he tripped when he hit me
and knocked himself out on the pavement.

798
01:16:34,590 --> 01:16:37,923
Next day, he kicked the crap outta me
till I cried like a baby...

799
01:16:37,993 --> 01:16:42,828
All right, come on, Arkansas.
You can't do this to yourself.

800
01:16:45,100 --> 01:16:48,092
I let 'em down.
I let my parents down...

801
01:16:48,170 --> 01:16:52,038
You didn't let anyone down. We're gonna
work this out. It's gonna be fine...

802
01:16:52,107 --> 01:16:54,268
Just stop it, Jake! OK?

803
01:16:54,343 --> 01:16:56,243
It's over.

804
01:16:58,580 --> 01:17:01,105
I don't belong here, OK?

805
01:17:01,183 --> 01:17:03,515
You belong here.

806
01:17:06,788 --> 01:17:09,723
I just need some time alone, all right?

807
01:17:10,726 --> 01:17:11,784
OK.

808
01:17:12,961 --> 01:17:14,258
All right.

809
01:17:45,127 --> 01:17:47,118
Switch.

810
01:17:53,068 --> 01:17:55,059
Thanks.

811
01:17:58,807 --> 01:18:00,468
You're ready, man.

812
01:18:03,779 --> 01:18:05,770
<i>(whistle)</i>

813
01:18:08,417 --> 01:18:10,112
<i>(whistle)</i>

814
01:18:10,185 --> 01:18:12,676
- Somebody jumped.
<i>- (whistle)</i>

