- Cool off. Cool off, Jake, come on.

819
01:18:50,158 --> 01:18:52,991
Take it easy. Just take it easy.
It's not worth it, man.

820
01:18:53,061 --> 01:18:55,757
Cool off, man. You gotta cool off.

821
01:19:45,680 --> 01:19:48,012
So you're quitting?

822
01:19:53,588 --> 01:19:56,216
