We both know how it's gonna end.

824
01:20:03,398 --> 01:20:08,131
I asked for more time
to prepare my statement for the board.

825
01:20:09,404 --> 01:20:13,272
Your appearance
has been moved to Monday.

826
01:20:13,341 --> 01:20:15,775
After the Brigade finals.

827
01:20:19,347 --> 01:20:23,113
I'm giving you
what you wanted all year, Huard.

828
01:20:56,685 --> 01:20:57,879
Hey.

829
01:20:58,053 --> 01:21:00,044
Hey.

830
01:21:03,658 --> 01:21:06,718
Doctor says you're gonna be all right.

831
01:21:08,730 --> 01:21:10,061
Jake.

832
01:21:10,498 --> 01:21:12,159
Yeah?

833
01:21:13,068 --> 01:21:15,400
What time's the fight?

834
01:21:17,873 --> 01:21:22,503
There are more important things
than the fight right now.

835
01:21:23,511 --> 01:21:26,105
Listen, Jake. We're both lucky.

836
01:21:28,450 --> 01:21:30,782
We got second chances.

837
01:21:35,190 --> 01:21:37,556
I'm not gonna waste mine.

838
01:21:40,495 --> 01:21:42,827
Neither are you.

839
01:21:46,067 --> 01:21:49,264
When you step in that ring,
you have three rounds

840
01:21:49,905 --> 01:21:52,237
