867
01:25:23,384 --> 01:25:27,787
- Get up, Jake.
...five, six, seven, eight.

868
01:25:30,525 --> 01:25:32,117
Attaboy, Jake.

869
01:25:33,061 --> 01:25:34,050
Box.

870
01:25:34,129 --> 01:25:36,154
<i>(Whitaker)</i> Here we go, baby.

871
01:25:36,598 --> 01:25:39,761
Stick and move. Stick and move.

872
01:25:39,834 --> 01:25:41,961
Put him down. Put him down.

873
