01:25:58,786 --> 01:26:01,846
<i>(Ali)</i> Defense, Jake. Hands up.

876
01:26:02,590 --> 01:26:06,321
<i>(Loo)</i> Get outta that corner.
Get outta the corner!

877
01:26:09,430 --> 01:26:11,091
<i>(bell)</i>

878
01:26:11,166 --> 01:26:12,633
Break. Break!

