907
01:30:20,415 --> 01:30:23,407
- Yeah! Stay down.
- Yeah, Jake!

908
01:30:23,484 --> 01:30:25,475
- One, two...
<i>- (Whitaker)</i> Get up, man.

909
01:30:25,553 --> 01:30:27,043
You're the champ. Come on.

910
01:30:27,121 --> 01:30:32,650
...five, six, seven, eight.
- He wants some more!

911
01:30:34,829 --> 01:30:36,160
Box.

912
01:30:39,700 --> 01:30:42,294
<i>(Ali)</i> There you go! Step around.

913
01:30:47,675 --> 01:30:49,506
Here we go.

914
01:30:52,180 --> 01:30:55,308
You got him, Jake. This is your time.

915
01:30:55,383 --> 01:30:57,408
<i>- (Whitaker)</i> Cole! Come on!
<i>- (Ali)</i> Yes!

916
01:30:57,485 --> 01:30:59,578
