917
01:30:59,654 --> 01:31:01,884
- Come on, Huard.
- Work him. He's going down.

918
01:31:01,956 --> 01:31:04,789
Just work the body.

919
01:31:04,859 --> 01:31:06,793
Let's go. 30 seconds.

920
01:31:10,031 --> 01:31:11,794
Go for it.

921
01:31:11,866 --> 01:31:12,958
Come on, Jake.

922
01:31:16,137 --> 01:31:20,574
He's getting tired, Jake.
You've gotta go for it. Go for it.

923
01:31:20,641 --> 01:31:22,438
<i>(Ali)</i> 20 seconds, Huard.

924
01:31:22,510 --> 01:31:24,808
Come on, Huard. Yeah!

925
01:31:25,746 --> 01:31:28,613
Keep your rhythm. Keep your rhythm.

926
01:31:28,683 --> 01:31:30,310
Get outta the corner.

927
01:31:30,885 --> 01:31:33,752
<i>(Loo)</i> Ten seconds, Jake.
You gotta take him out now.

928
01:31:33,821 --> 01:31:35,311
Come on, Huard.

929
01:31:37,959 --> 01:31:40,450
<i>- (Loo)</i> Go after him, Jake.
<i>- (Ali)</i> Go, go, go!

930
01:31:47,502 --> 01:31:49,663
<i>- (bell)</i>
- Break. Break.

931
01:31:53,741 --> 01:31:56,369
<i>(Loo)</i> Great fight, Jake.

932
01:31:56,444 --> 01:31:59,242
Yeah, that kid Huard's a tough kid.

933
01:32:02,984 --> 01:32:05,885
- Go on, Jake!
- That's my boy right there.

934
01:32:05,953 --> 01:32:08,285
That's my boy.

935
01:32:11,492 --> 01:32:14,586
OK. Fighters to the centre.

936
01:32:14,662 --> 01:32:17,495
Fighters to the centre. Let's go.

937
01:32:31,045 --> 01:32:33,741
- Out the way.
- Let me get a shot.

938
01:32:36,551 --> 01:32:38,985
Sorry, man.

939
01:32:41,088 --> 01:32:43,682
I told you. Hell of a fight.

940
01:32:43,758 --> 01:32:47,023
Yeah, number one, baby.
Yeah, number one.

941
01:32:54,802 --> 01:32:57,464
You did great.

942
01:32:58,439 --> 01:33:01,602
<i>(crowd chanting. "Jake! Jake!")</i>

943
01:33:07,782 --> 01:33:09,807
- Good job, man.
- Good job, Huard.

944
01:33:11,419 --> 01:33:14,980
- Good job, man.
- Good job, Jake. Good fight.

