951
01:34:15,883 --> 01:34:19,717
Punishment will commence immediately
upon your return from summer cruise.

952
01:34:19,787 --> 01:34:21,982
Is that understood?

953
01:34:23,357 --> 01:34:25,484
Sir, yes, sir.

954
01:34:37,938 --> 01:34:40,736
Congratulations, Midshipman Huard.

955
01:34:40,808 --> 01:34:43,003
Thank you, sir.

956
01:34:46,047 --> 01:34:48,345
Class of 2008.

